caption.text:
I don't know this feeling. feeling happy ? Yeah. feeling sad ? Yeah. Feel happy because I was given the opportunity by The Almighty, become a joy to others. Given the opportunity also could improve again to become a better person. Feel sad because when I celebrate my birthday, I realized I was getting older, and there is a burden, what I had done. Feel sad too because maybe people who close to me could not celebrate my birthday. For the umpteenth time I'm always sad when my friends did not come to celebrate my birthday. Get mad when my close friend didn't say happy birthday. How silly I am to imagine all of that. I'm getting older, I realized that I have to understand them. Not only one who should I understand but all of them. Because I realized they had every reason.  Sometimes i really thank to the Lord because the more i am mature, the more i am realize every single mistake i had made. For all person who care thanks for sharing the story to me, parents, family, friends and everyone. 
Dear God. Thank You for another day in my life. I promise  I'll become the best for You, cause everything I do is only for You 😊😊😊
